			This entry was posted<span class="by-author"> by <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://elidourado.com/blog/author/elidourado/" title="View all posts by Eli Dourado" rel="author">Eli Dourado</a></span></span> on <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/replies-to-interfluidity/" title="9:55 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-08-16T09:55:43+00:00">August 16, 2012</time></a>.<br /><a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/" style="text-decoration:none"><i class="fa fa-tags"></i></a> <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/chapter-17/" rel="tag">Chapter 17</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/inequality/" rel="tag">inequality</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/interfluidity/" rel="tag">Interfluidity</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/landsburg/" rel="tag">Landsburg</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/macroeconomics/" rel="tag">macroeconomics</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/monetary-policy/" rel="tag">monetary policy</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/public-choice/" rel="tag">public choice</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/waldman/" rel="tag">Waldman</a>, <a href="http://elidourado.com/blog/tag/weininger/" rel="tag">Weininger</a><br /><i class="fa fa-btc"></i> Tip via Bitcoin at <a href="bitcoin:1FMxbQLh2hEoWXgM4GggbSAMoR61iL7zdp"> 1FMxbQLh2hEoWXgM4GggbSAMoR61iL7zdp </a>											</footer><!-- .entry-meta -->
